text.string: TATA Power Southern Odisha Distribution Limited
Chhattisgarh State Power Distribution Company Limited

1. ALL DIMENSIONS ARE IN MILLIMETERS AND LEVEL ARE IN METERS. 2. FOLLOW WRITTEN DIMENSIONS ONLY. DO NOT SCALE THE DRAWING. 3. FINISHED FLOOR LEVEL (F.F.L) I.E SHALL BE 300MM. ABOVE THE H.P.P. 4. ALL FINISH FLOOR LEVELS (EXTERNAL/INTERNAL) MUST BE LAID IN PROPER SLOPE & DIRECTION AS MAY BE REQUIRED AS PER NORMAL ENGINEERING PRACTICE. 5. PLINTH PROTECTION (750 MM WIDE) SHOULD BE PROVIDED ALL AROUND THE BUILDING AS PER SPECIFICATIONS. 6. ALL CHHAJJA / CANOPY PROJECTIONS SHALL HAVE DRIP MOULD GROOVES. 7. ELECTRICAL AND SERVICES DETAIL TO BE AS PER APPROVED SPECIFICATIONS AND DRAWINGS.
H.P.P. - HIGHEST PAVEMENT POINT F.F.L - FINISHED FLOOR LEVEL T.O.C - TOP OF CONCRETE B.O.L. - BOTTOM OF LINTEL R.W.P - RAIN WATER PIPE TYP. - TYPICAL
